import React, { useState } from "react"
//import Secondpage from "./Secondpage"

import Navigation from "./Navigation"
import "./Style2.css"

import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import img from "./logo_.png"
//import {FiUser} from "react-icons/fi"
import { FcGoogle } from "react-icons/fc"
import { ImFacebook2 } from "react-icons/im"
import { AiFillLinkedin } from "react-icons/ai"
import Button from "@restart/ui/esm/Button"
const Student = () => {

    const [Forgoat, setForgoat] = useState(false)
    const [Login,setLogin] = useState(false)
    
    return (

        <>
            <Row>
                <Navigation />
            </Row>
            {
                !Forgoat ?  !Login ?
                    <Row>
                        <Col></Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Row className="mt-5" >Click here to login this page</Row>
                            <Row className="mt-5">
                                <button className="loginButton" onClick={() => { setForgoat(true) }} >Forgoat </button>
                                <button className="loginButton" onClick={() => { setLogin(true) }} > Login</button>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                        <Col></Col>
                    </Row>
                    :
                    <Row>
                        <Col></Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Row className="mt-2" >Email ID :</Row>
                            <Row className="mt-2">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Student Name" className="email" />
                            </Row>
                            <Row className="mt-2" >User-Name :</Row>
                            <Row className="mt-2">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="User-Name" className="email" />
                            </Row>
                            <Row className="mt-2" >Password:</Row>
                            <Row className="mt-2">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Password" className="password" />
                            </Row>

                            <Row className="mt-2">
                                <button className="loginButton" onClick={() => { setForgoat(false) }}>Login</button>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                        <Col></Col>
                    </Row>
:
<Row onClick={() => { setLogin(false) }}> This is login part</Row>
                    

            }


<Row className="mt-5 mx-3">
                                We believe in helping the underpriveledged children to outshine themselves in this world
                                and get all the benefits that a normal child gets.We majorly focus on the financially backward children,
                                to get the education and other like healthcare,
                                nutrition, protection, and response in the time of emergencies.
                            </Row>

        </>

    )
}
export default Student
